title: HOUR 1 - Green Bay Packers, Trent Dilfer
itunes:title: HOUR 1 - Green Bay Packers, Trent Dilfer
description:
In hour 1, Colin gives his opinion on how the Packers are desperate for leadership and seem to have gotten soft under Matt LaFleur. The Eagles may have won the division with last nights victory over the Cowboys. Trent Dilfer joins to talk the Packers woes, Tampa Bay and more.
